{"tha-ap561:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap561:0.2":"Yasavagga ","tha-ap561:0.3":"Sivakattheraapadana ","tha-ap561:1.1":"“Esanaya carantassa, ","tha-ap561:1.2":"vipassissa mahesino; ","tha-ap561:1.3":"Rittakam pattam disvana, ","tha-ap561:1.4":"kummasam purayim aham. ","tha-ap561:2.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap561:2.2":"yam bhikkhamadadim tada; ","tha-ap561:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap561:2.4":"kummasassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap561:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap561:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap561:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap561:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap561:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap561:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap561:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap561:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap561:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap561:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sivakatthero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap561:7.1":"Sivakattherassapadanam navamam. "}